{"tid":1451530,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"武力升級係我地唯一出路","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:35:30.000Z","uid":172616,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"155113954c1592a34ebb050f9e5b955dc67c01e4","tid":1451530,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:18:58.000Z","msg":"班畜生<br />\n開槍打頭打眼<br />\n室內出催淚彈<br />\n亂棍打人<br />\n出動臥底拉人<br />\n<br />\n佢地嘅每一個行動唔係以拘捕為大前題<br />\n佢地係想傷害人<br />\n想殺人<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁<br />\n我地再維持喺不合作和平理性亦都冇意義<br />\n<br />\n只有武器升級先有可能打低佢地<br />\n冇錯<br />\n係打倒政府<br />\n咁多日嚟大家有眼見<br />\n政府嘅態度就係死撐<br />\n打死唔跪<br />\n一個訴求都唔會應承<br />\n只有重新組建一個完全民選政府先可能破解當前局面<br />\n<br />\n要重新組建就只有武裝起義一個方法<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講民意，會支持嘅已經行晒出嚟<br />\n唔支持嘅就無論如何都唔會撐"},{"pid":"d95f87349a1f6f31ec47e12508bf77a45c0ede67","tid":1451530,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c66d93763f6fe0ab668d61217dbe6fbd4eb8a5e","tid":1451530,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:23:54.000Z","msg":"入機場"},{"pid":"13e86d15d825cd86974dac49264f5db2cd299997","tid":1451530,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c66d93763f6fe0ab668d61217dbe6fbd4eb8a5e","tid":1451530,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:23:54.000Z","msg":"入機場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:24:09.000Z","msg":"一定入"},{"pid":"8484cbb35efe575487cd322b589850cd480cb303","tid":1451530,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13e86d15d825cd86974dac49264f5db2cd299997","tid":1451530,"uid":172616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c66d93763f6fe0ab668d61217dbe6fbd4eb8a5e","tid":1451530,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:23:54.000Z","msg":"入機場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:24:09.000Z","msg":"一定入"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"一齊叫人唔好再鳩坐"},{"pid":"b1